Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到20%的人愿意看到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Less than 20% are comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統和副總統有任何親屬關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}with a president and a vice president being related in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到10%的人支持從未當選過公職的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Less than 10% approve of someone who's never held elected office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我們能扭轉局面呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But if we can move the needle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提升40個百分點嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Forty points?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看我們怎么說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's how we frame it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的支持率不錯  比我還高\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Her favorables are decent. They're better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對人不對事  就她作為聯合國大使而言\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}In a void, but when it comes to her time as the UN ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持率就猛跌了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}they fall off a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表現和經驗是重要因素\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Performance and experience are big factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們得強調她的優點而非軟肋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then we have to amplify her strengths, not her weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要一個有價值的副總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're looking for a VP who's an asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這項調查表明她不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This research proves she isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作不是勸我放棄  而是想辦法說服大家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Your job is not to dissuade me, but to figure out how we sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  可選的人很多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, there are so many people to choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果目標是獲選\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If the goal is to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們在不遺余力...  -賽斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- and we're bending over backwards-- -Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統要我們制定計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president asked us to develop a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就制定計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}so that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我辦公室等我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll meet you in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-您知道他是對的  -當然了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You know he's right. - Well, of course he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們可以給她點別的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Maybe we offer something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不會聽的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉安呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What about LeAnn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在考慮那個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, I was thinking that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是怎么讓她配合\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Question is how to co-opt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她喜歡支票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She likes paychecks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  光錢不行  她想要政治影響力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's gotta be more than money. She wants coattails.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟克萊爾交換\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We swap Claire's for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-競選經理嗎  -我們需要新鮮血液\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Campaign manager? - We could use some fresh blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我同意  但莉安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That I agree with, but LeAnn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法保證我們能控制她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, there's no guarantee that we can control her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果她能說服克萊爾改主意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah, but if she can convince Claire to change her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那對我就足夠了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰況室都等您了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They're ready for you in the Situation Room, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就過去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有必要你可以跟她合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You could work with her if you had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不非得喜歡她才能跟她合作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't have to like her to work with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很好  打電話吧  -您還想讓賽斯知情嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Good, make the call. - You still want Seth on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  直到莉安同意  我需要擔心他嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, until LeAnn's on board. Do I have to worry about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們挖得很深  他的電郵和手機記錄沒問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We dug pretty deep. Nothing in his emails or phone records.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他聰明  知道掩蓋蹤跡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's smart enough to cover his tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟他談談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你覺得這幅畫如何  -我不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What do you think of this painting? - I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃克和我有一晚曾坐在這里  盯著掛在這兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Walker and I sat here one night, stared up at a painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在總統辦公室的那副藍色的畫看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the blue one that's in the Oval now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這副是后換的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They replaced it with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是美國國旗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's not the American flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是南軍的旗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's the rebel flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉入虛無\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}sinking into oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是閃電嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is that a lightning bolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為是的...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, I assume...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非是想把船畫成獨角獸還沒畫好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Unless it's just a bad attempt at making the ship a unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看出來了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色彩不錯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Colors are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不喜歡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也不喜歡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I guess I hate it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在白宮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I suppose it's not a good idea to have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掛聯邦旗大概不是個好主意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the Confederate flag hanging here in the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其經歷了南卡的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}after everything that's happened in South Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然它是在下沉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Even if it is sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得我們該掛什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do you think we should put up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  您更喜歡的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. Something you like better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶那支我簽字的馬克筆了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you have that marker I sign things with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的手放在墻上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Put your hand up on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生  -放在墻上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Sir? - Put it on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指伸開一點\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Spread your fingers a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Wait. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  今天就玩到這兒吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yeah... That's enough fun for today. -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格  我不知道該怎么做到他要我做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug, I don't know how to do what he's asking me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒有魔法...  -泄露事件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- There is not some magical-- - The leaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是你嗎  -你認真的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Was it you? - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常認真\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像其他人一樣上交了我的通訊記錄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I handed over all of my correspondence, just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不能證明什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doesn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在挽救他的競選\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm trying to save this campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想搞破壞  讓總統自己來就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If I wanted to sabotage it, I'd let the president do it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是在副總統的事上跟他對著干\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}instead of fighting back on this VP thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許那只是裝樣子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Or that's just a cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年你不在的時候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've been in the trenches for the past year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在第一線  現在你還懷疑我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}while you've been gone, and now you doubt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要這套\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得到這份工作是靠挖丑事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You got this job by digging up dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你到現在還不信任我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you can't trust me by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我還在這兒干嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't know what I'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說你想辭職嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you saying you wanna resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我最不想的了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That is the last thing that I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你沒有給我留下的動力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but you're not giving me any incentive to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  去它的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right. Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽斯  我現在選擇信任你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Seth, I'm choosing to believe you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我有一日感到后悔了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but if I come to regret that decision--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會的  因為不是我干的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You won't, because it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是認為密查姆有可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I still think it could be Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你確定  -完全確定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You're sure? - I'm positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統也確定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And so is the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以走了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}May I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是你想談談第一夫人的計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Or did you want to discuss the plan for the First Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打電話  我稍后去你辦公室\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I have some calls to make. I'll come to your office after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我接莉安·哈維\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Get me LeAnn Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米爾金將住在他家  安東·考斯基\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Milkin will be staying with this man, Anton Khalski.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他原本擁有俄羅斯第二大的銀行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He owned the second-largest bank in Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到2013年被佩特羅夫查抄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}until Petrov seized it in 2013.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考斯基逃出國境去了愛沙尼亞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Khalski fled across the border to Estonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們讓米爾金的飛機飛往首都塔林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We'll have Milkin's plane fly to Tallinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他會乘船去薩拉馬考斯基的夏季別墅\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}then he'll travel by boat to Khalski's summer house on Saaremaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  我們將解凍米爾金的美國財產\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tomorrow we'll unfreeze Milkin's American assets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并轉移至考斯基的瑞士賬戶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and transfer them to Khalski's Swiss accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考斯基會聯絡他的俄羅斯軍隊朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Khalski will reach out to his Russian military friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后開始收買他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and then start buying them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄聯邦安全局在監控考斯基嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are the FSB monitoring Khalski?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密切監控  他們會知道是我們在支持他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Closely. They'll know we're behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-莫斯科如果質問我們呢  -當然是否認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- When Moscow confronts us? - We'll deny, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果佩特羅夫反應過激  我們是否有所準備\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are we prepared if Petrov overreacts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六艦隊在博斯普魯斯海峽附近有部屬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The Sixth Fleet has a presence near the Bosphorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在北海也有巡航\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we have patrols in the North Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-起草命令吧  -先生  可以說一句嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Draft the order. - Sir, if I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們討論過了  凱茜  -是的  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Yeah, we've discussed this, Cathy. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我必須\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I feel obligated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要提出強烈的反對  這將給我們帶來的外交影響\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to raise my very strong objections. The diplomatic cost to us--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果外交好用\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If diplomacy were working,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本就不需要考慮這么做了  是吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we wouldn't have to consider this course of action, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我已經提出了擔憂  -謝謝大家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I've voiced my concerns. - Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會突然讓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're not going to surprise me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統接電話打我個措手不及吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}by putting the president on, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只有我們  但他告訴我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, it's just us. He filled me in, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-關于第一夫人的要求  -怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- on the First Lady's request. - And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想讓你當競選經理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We wanna make you campaign manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的郵件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Look at your email.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是什么  -我們的調研\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What is this? - Our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果是一樣的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It all boils down to the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做了幾個民調  又如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You ran a few polls, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還有焦點小組  -毫無意義\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Focus groups, too. - Meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么低的數字可不是毫無意義\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊爾不能參選  你很清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Claire can't be on the ticket. You know she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事不是孤立的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This isn't something you can isolate on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果油價飆升至6美元/加侖  你們就完了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If gas prices hit $6 a gallon, you're fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你們會失去所有關鍵人群  -我們很清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You lose every key demo. - We're well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果總統讓克萊爾做他的競選搭檔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But if the president makes Claire his running mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么話題會轉向策略而非經濟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it makes the conversation tactical instead of economic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就給了你們時間處理俄羅斯危機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That buys you time on the Russia crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們解決了那事  對總統的自信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You solve that, confidence in the president
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能轉變成對總統選擇的自信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}translates into confidence in his choice--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打給你不是想聽你游說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I didn't call you to be convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打來是想給你份工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I called to offer you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是為了拆安德伍德夫人的臺  -不僅是因為她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Only to get to Mrs. Underwood. -This isn't just about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要你  你能扭轉競選局勢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We need you. You'll turn this campaign around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好驚訝  道格  我以為你不怎么喜歡我呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm surprised, Doug. I didn't think you were very fond of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡人才  總統也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm fond of talent. So is the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忠于第一夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My loyalty is to the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只求你跟她談談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All I'm asking is that you talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣吧  如果你把我的調查給總統看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll tell you what. I'll show Claire your research
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你的調查給克萊爾看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}if you show the president mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我可以同意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不該跟你說話的  希瑟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I shouldn't even be talking to you, Heather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常擔憂有濫用職權的現象\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm seriously concerned that there's been an abuse of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司法部長女士  斯坦普先生可以見您了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Madam Attorney General? Mr. Stamper, um, is ready to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得掛了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責行動的探員\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The agent in charge of the operation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后馬上得到了晉升\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}got a promotion directly after.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽著  -瑪莎  如果總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Listen-- - Martha, if the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或他的手下  如果有人強迫聯調局\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or one of his staff... If anyone strong-armed the bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追查盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}into pursuing Lucas Goodwin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道  那就是濫用職權\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}then you know that's an abuse of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就為總統工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I work for the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正要跟他的幕僚長面談\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I am about to sit down with his Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法律就是法律  -這是政治  不是法律\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- The law is the law. - This is politics, not the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  你讓我擔任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not true. You brought me on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副檢察長是因為我正直\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as solicitor general because of my integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我來找你  是因為你也一樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I am bringing this to you because of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司法部長女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Madam Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的得掛了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I really need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果古德溫的故事有一絲真實性\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If a sliver of Goodwin's story holds up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How did you even find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的對手研究團隊聯絡過證人保護計劃的人嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Did your oppo team speak to someone in WITSEC?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那樣  這種違法行為...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Because if that's the case, then that sort of breach is not--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我跟他本人談過  -什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I spoke to him myself, personally. - You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他來找我的  他找到了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He came to me. He tracked me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要沾這事  希瑟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not touching this, Heather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格  真是抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒事  -我剛剛在跟首席法官通話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- No-- - I was just on with the Chief Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒事的  快進來吧  -謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Don't be silly, come on in. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-這邊請  -謝謝你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- This way. - Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  她當大使時表現可不怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't know. She didn't do that well as ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經驗不夠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She wasn't experienced enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  她做過大使\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hold on, she was an ambassador?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聯合國大使  -克里斯  你不看新聞嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- At the United Nations. - Chris, don't you watch the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們多少人也有同感\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How many of you feel the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了缺乏經驗  有其他原因嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Any other reasons, besides lack of experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在莫斯科情緒失控時很沖動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, she was really impulsive when she had that outburst in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她根本就不該去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, she never should've been there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參議院都否決了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, the Senate voted her down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她丈夫還是任命了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and then her husband just appoints her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪能這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  我喜歡她這個人  但我同意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay, see, I like her as a person, but I agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她該繼續做她的第一夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}she should stick to being First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是希望你來勸我放棄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, he's hoping you'll convince me to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能掙得比你給的多得多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Look, I'd make a killing compared to what you've paid me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們談過要有所成就\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but you and I talked about making a real mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親真的很喜歡弗蘭西斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My father really liked Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作為我父親  我們結婚前一天  他跟我說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But as my daddy, he said to me, the day before we got married,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你只有一次人生  克萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"You have one life, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定你要跟這個男人共度此生嗎"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you sure this is the man you wanna spend it with?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么說的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我不想在懷疑中度過人生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I said I didn't want to live my life full of doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得弗蘭西斯想讓我懷疑自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, I think Francis wants me to doubt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么回事  -我母親  殺蜥蜴呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What was that? - My mother... killing a lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我給您開門  夫人  -我自己能開\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I'll get the door for you, ma'am. - I can open the door myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心腳下  地上有血\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Watch your step. There's blood on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你親自把這個交給總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I want you to take this to the president, in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-如果可以  今晚飛過去  -當然\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Try to get on a plane tonight if you can. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This one's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是溫的  -至少是免費的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- It's warm. - At least it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許得要你們兌現保險了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I may need to cash in my insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她拿下提名  我會得到什么位置\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tell me what my position would be if she wins the nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是司法部長嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is it the attorney general?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -算了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- The what? - Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做競選搭檔嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}For running mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在考慮競選搭檔太早了  他還沒贏呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's way too early for running mates. He hasn't even won.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們說的是一件事嗎  -你先說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Are we talking about the same thing? - You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事不是那么辦的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It doesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你想找工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, you're the one looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要么告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can either involve me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么就等著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or you can start reading
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙頭條報道鄧巴泄露婚姻消息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}headlines about Dunbar pushing a marriage story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那會害死你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That would blow you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格已經起疑了  我沒什么好怕的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug's already suspicious. I've got nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盧卡斯·古德溫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lucas Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是《先驅報》的編輯  是那個...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He was an editor... at The Herald, the one who--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們跟他談過  -他不是在蹲監獄嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- We spoke to him. - Isn't he in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將于9:30出發\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's scheduled to depart at 0930 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破曉前不久就能到塔林\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That'll put him in Tallinn shortly before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的站長與去薩拉馬的護送隊在待命了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Our station chief is standing by with the escort to Saaremaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是行政命令\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is the executive order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-長官  -凱茜  我已經決定了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Sir-- - Cathy, I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他到達后每小時報告一次  -是  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Hourly updates once he lands. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴道格我準備好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tell Doug I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐吧  莉安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Please, have a seat, LeAnn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興你同意加入了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm delighted you've agreed to come on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據我所知是有條件的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's my understanding there is a condition attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明白這個條件吧  你跟她談過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And she understands that condition? You've spoken with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生  我沒說清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, my apologies, sir. I wasn't clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指我們的條件  不是你們的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I meant our condition, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在初選日\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}On Super Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么大老遠親自送來啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's a long trip to deliver this in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, it's not the sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能落入旁人手中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}you'd want to end up in the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要留在華盛頓嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Are you staying here in Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我馬上回去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, I'm going straight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么話需要我帶給第一夫人嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is there anything you'd like me to tell the First Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴她今晚就能回復她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Tell her she'll have her answer by this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸程一路順風  哈維小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have a safe trip back, Ms. Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己出去吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll show myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當長的一段時間以來  我和總統已經漸漸疏遠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}For quite some time, the president and I have been growing apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓密查姆進來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Have Meechum step in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們曾企圖挽救我們的婚姻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've attempted to save our marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但雖經過很多努力  我最終認識到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but after great effort, I've come to the conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的婚姻已不可挽救\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that it can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天很遺憾地宣布\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It is with great regret that I announce today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將申請離婚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm filing for divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們得阻止她  -在她到機場之前嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- We have to stop her. - Before she gets to the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  克萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, I mean Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您找我  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You asked for me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機和固話...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Both the cell and the landline--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進入了封鎖  夫人  我們屏蔽了...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're on lockdown, ma'am. We had to scramble all the--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封鎖  你在說什么呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Lockdown? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您待在房內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm gonna need you to stay in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -抱歉  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What-- - I'm sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能強迫我留在屋內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can't force me to stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有針對您很可信的威脅...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There is a current, highly credible threat to your life--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你的上級說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I need to speak to your supervising--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是您在達拉斯的保安主管  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I am the head of your detail here in Dallas, ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到命令要保護您安全留在屋內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I've been ordered to keep you securely in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德伍德加油\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Go Underwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-聽啊  -笨蛋伍德  笨蛋伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Listen. - Blunderwood! Blunderwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道他們喊什么嗎  "笨蛋伍德"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you know what they're chanting? "Blunderwood."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是他們的英語教授\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And if I were their English professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給他們的小聰明打A\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}why, I would give them all an "A" for cleverness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但準確性打D\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...but a "D" for accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但做總統就是如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But that's part of being president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會樹敵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You make enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家此刻就能聽到我的一些敵人在外面吶喊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and you can hear some of mine just outside, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我很感激你們每個人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, I am grateful to each and every one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天前來表示對我的支持\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}for coming out and showing your support today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們  我們能拿到提名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's because of you we will win this nomination,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我今天來你們大學\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and that's why I came to your college today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, of course, I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天會有抗議者來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that there would be protesters here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本可以不來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and I could've chosen not to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以選擇離開時避開他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or I could choose to avoid them as I leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不打算那么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I'm not going to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為外面那些學生  你們的同學\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because those students out there, your fellow classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是他們的總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm their president, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他們是不是為我投票  我也得帶領他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And whether they vote for me or not, I have to lead them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  一定得傾聽他們  跟他們說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, it's important to hear them, to talk to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽他們的想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to listen to their ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為就像你們在大學學習\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because, just as you're learning in college,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思想的多樣化讓我們都更加明智\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}a diversity of ideas makes us all wiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你們的總統來說也是如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and that holds true even for your president.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的領導\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}True leadership
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是逃避與你意見相左的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}is not running away from those who disagree with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要接納他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but embracing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天結束后  我就打算這么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and that is exactly what I intend to do when I'm done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出去接納那群人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm gonna go out and embrace that entire crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不該坐軍用飛機嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Shouldn't we be taking a military plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那會吸引注意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That would draw attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都安排好了  你不會有事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Everything's been worked out. You're in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  睡會兒吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Here, get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚要走很久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's gonna be a long trip tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋伍德  笨蛋伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Blunderwood! Blunderwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有消息嗎  -都安排好了  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Any news? - Everything's secure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們愛你  安德伍德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We love you, Underwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝大家前來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you all for coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括那些不完全支持我的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}even those of you who don't entirely support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-總統先生你真棒  -謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Way to go, Mr. President! - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想盡量聽聽你們究竟反對我什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I wanna try to hear what it is that you disagree with me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道不是每個人都支持我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I understand not everyone's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-停止戰爭  -滾回加夫尼去吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- No more wars! - Go back to Gaffney!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎  謝謝你能來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hello, how are you? Thank you for coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  謝謝你能來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hello, thank you for coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你很棒  -我們知道你的真實面目\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You're doing a great job! - We know what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我來是想聽聽你們的聲音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right, I'm here to try to listen to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一個一個說可能會比較好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but probably one at a time is gonna be a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們應該進行一對一的對話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay, maybe we could have a conversation, more one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很難聽清\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's difficult to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你們不喜歡什么  但你們支持什么呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I understand what you don't believe in, but what are you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣問也許比較好  你怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That would be a good question. All right, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經沖我喊了有一會兒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You've been yelling at me for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得我該在哪些方面有所改變\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What do you think I should be doing differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你應該辭職  -好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You should resign. - Well, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒在請求你為我投票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not asking for your vote,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你是總統  你會怎么做呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but what would you do if you were president?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在毀掉我們的國家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You're ruining our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來這里是想聽你們的心聲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I came out here to try to listen to what you wanna say,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你們只是一直尖叫下去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but if all you're gonna do is scream--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有槍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快走  -快帶他走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Let's go! - Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快走  快走  -走走走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Move! Move! - Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人企圖刺殺總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There has been an attempted assassination of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭克·安德伍德總統遭到了槍擊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}President Frank Underwood has been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約十分鐘前發生于華盛頓特區\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It occurred about ten minutes ago during a campaign event
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈蒙德大學的一場競選活動中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}at Hammond University in Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們尚不清楚總統的傷情有多重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We do not yet know how severely the president has been wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在被送往杰弗遜紀念醫院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He is en route to Jefferson Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不知道他的情況有多嚴重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't know how serious his condition may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺殺未遂事件的視頻還沒送到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Footage of the assassination attempt is still making its way to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但相信很快就能夠公布\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and we expect to have that shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目擊者聲稱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Witnesses are reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時有連續好幾聲槍響\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that there was a quick succession of gunshots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約有四五發\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}four or five,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍手是一個人  身份還未確認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}a lone gunman whose identity we are still trying to determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已得知槍手已被擊斃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've been told the gunman was killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另有至少一名特勤人員遇難\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as well as at least one Secret Service agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.05,0:22:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們還未得到明確證實\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but we don't have definitive confirmation of that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不清楚槍手和特勤人員的身份\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't yet know who the gunman may be or who the agent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -總統遇刺了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- What's happened? - The president's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導播現在告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm hearing now that the president
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統至少腹部中了一槍  也許不止\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}received at least one gunshot to the abdomen, possibly more,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他緊捂腹部\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that he clutched his stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即倒地\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that he fell instantly to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現場尖叫連連  人群陷入恐慌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and there were screams, people panicking,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,場面十分混亂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that it has been very chaotic at that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我們獲得的消息很有限\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We have very little information at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅知道總統遭遇槍擊受傷\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}other than shots were fired, the president wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如我所言  他還活著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But as I say, he is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也還沒得到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We've gotten no official
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮的官方聲明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}statement from the White House as of yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了解總統的具體情況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}either the president's precise condition
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是布萊斯副總統的行蹤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}or the whereabouts of Vice President Blythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息稱他目前在白宮  但我們還不能確認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He is believed to be at the White House. We cannot confirm that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不清楚他是否會出任代總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}nor do we know if he will take over as acting president,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵照憲法第25條修正案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}assuming the duties of the presidency under the terms
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承擔總統的職責\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}of the 25th Amendment to the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果總統的傷勢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}That would seem likely, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我們認為的那樣嚴重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}if the president's wounds are as serious
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將很有可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as we believe them to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是國家的艱難時刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is a difficult moment for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我國總統第一次遇刺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It is not the first time that a president has been shot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和很多人此前都曾經歷過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}in my lifetime or in many of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便對那些經歷過這種事的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But even for those of us who have experienced this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事仍觸目驚心  駭人聽聞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it is no less of a shock, it is no less terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是檢驗我國堅韌的時刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It is the moment when our nation's resilience,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢驗人民團結的時刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}when our collective strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最能檢驗一切的時刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the moment when all of that is tested the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們難以想象\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And we can only imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人此時多么痛苦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}how difficult it must be for the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-弗蘭西斯他...  -邁克爾說了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Francis-- - Michael told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得回華盛頓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I have to go back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.62,0:24:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你還耽擱什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還指望我安慰你嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Do you expect me to console you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我只是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再見  母親  -克萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Goodbye, Mother. - Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望他死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I hope he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.60,0:24:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊爾  我無法想象你多么難過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Claire, I can't imagine how difficult this must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我幫忙嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你來電慰問  副總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I appreciate the call, Mr. Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你眼下肯定還有許多事得處理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but I'm sure you've got a lot to take care of right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要我的幫助嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is there anything I can do to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.55,0:24:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我們弄清目前的狀況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be making a brief appearance once we have a better sense of...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.90,0:25:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就會進行簡短發言\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}where things stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.76,0:25:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我在場嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Would you like me to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.39,0:25:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣最好  讓國家見到第一夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think it would be good, the country seeing the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.62,0:25:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得讓他們見到你臨危不亂更重要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I think it's more important that they see your steady hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在我身邊  我會更有底氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If you're by my side, it would certainly make it steadier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.38,0:25:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  我都聽你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Of course. Anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會為你們祈禱  為你們倆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm gonna be praying for you. For both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.26,0:25:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  唐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.55,0:25:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.36,0:26:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.58,0:26:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有高度機密事務\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The acting president needs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.38,0:26:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要向代總統報告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to be briefed on a highly classified matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.96,0:26:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有軍事機密權限的人請離開房間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Everyone without military clearance, we'll need the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍手開了兩槍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was in fact two shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一槍擦傷了身體  就在右臂之下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}One that grazed the torso just beneath the right arm
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.95,0:26:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一槍射入了腹部\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and the second which entered the abdomen,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.57,0:26:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半傷了肝臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}possibly into his liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.05,0:27:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然是這一槍造成了最嚴重的傷害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Obviously, it was that shot that did the greatest damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.53,0:27:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據悉  總統目前情況危急\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president is currently reported to be in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.91,0:27:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為保護總統遇害的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The Secret Service agent
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.17,0:27:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特勤局特工名叫艾德華·密查姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that was killed protecting the president was Edward Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.08,0:27:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是總統安保隊隊長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He is the head of the president's detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.84,0:27:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在可以確定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and we can confirm that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.02,0:27:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他中槍后  在死前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}After being shot and before he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死了身份仍未知的襲擊者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}he killed the assailant whose identity is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在等待白宮新聞發言人賽斯·格雷森\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're waiting now on a press conference from the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召開新聞發布會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}from Press Secretary Seth Grayson,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.06,0:27:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發布會稍后就將舉行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and we expect to have that beginning in just a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.69,0:27:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先給我看過兩遍  再對外確認\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We confirm nothing unless you run it past me twice first,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.09,0:27:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不希望...  -格雷森先生...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I don't want-- - Mr. Grayson...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.22,0:27:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上過去  不要有任何傳言  只要事實\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm on my way. We don't want any rumors, only facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.48,0:27:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有名學生宣稱是特勤局的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's a student who's claiming it was the Secret Service
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.16,0:27:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-開的第一槍  -我剛說了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- who fired the first shot. - What did I just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.36,0:27:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-別拿這種屁話浪費我時間  -先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Do not waste my time with that bullshit. - Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒體在等了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}the press is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.77,0:27:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行  我馬上過去  我的...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right, I'm... I'm coming. Uh, where's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.95,0:27:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日午后12:38  副總統唐納德·布萊斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}At 12:38 this afternoon, Vice President Donald Blythe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.13,0:27:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由內閣任命為代總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}was authorized as acting president by the cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.74,0:27:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前他正與內閣會面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He is currently meeting with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.80,0:28:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約20分鐘前  第一夫人在安德魯空軍基地降落\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Approximately 20 minutes ago, the First Lady landed at Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不久就會達到醫院\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She is expected to arrive at the hospital shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.35,0:28:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-安德伍德夫人  -他怎么樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Mrs. Underwood. - How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.18,0:28:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還在手術室里  大概還得要幾小時\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They're still in the OR. Probably a few hours left to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.79,0:28:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能保住命嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Is he going to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被直接擊中肝臟  肝臟部分破裂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He took a direct hit to his liver, which is partially shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.07,0:28:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運的是  左葉有一部分幾乎完好無損\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Fortunately, part of the left lobe is mostly intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.18,0:28:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們認為  他有很大幾率挺過手術\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, we think there's a decent chance he will survive surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.04,0:28:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便如此  真正的難關在術后才開始\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but even if he does, that's when the real fight begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.94,0:28:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想見他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd like to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.70,0:28:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術一結束我就告訴您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}As soon as he's out, I'll make sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.11,0:29:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建議取消這次行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'd recommend we call off this operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.86,0:29:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓飛機調頭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we turn the plane around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.59,0:29:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不同意  我們精心計劃過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I disagree. It's well planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.68,0:29:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且總統已經簽字了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president already signed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.93,0:29:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統可能挺不過來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-國務卿女士  -不準這樣說  凱茜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Madam Secretary... - We'll have no talk like that, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.66,0:29:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My apologies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.97,0:29:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說的是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What I am trying to say is that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,針鋒相對的風險太大了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}it is too risky to antagonize--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.41,0:29:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目的是嚇唬他們  不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The point was to scare them, not--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.92,0:29:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最高指揮官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}To do anything of this nature
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.38,0:29:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法工作時做這種事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}while the commander in chief is incapacitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-俄羅斯人會利用這時機  -我們現在高度警戒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- the Russians will take advantage-- - We're at high alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.92,0:29:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們準備好面對一切可能了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're prepared for all eventualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.53,0:29:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不能把軍隊當成故障保險\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We don't want the military to be the fail-safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.66,0:29:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副...總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. Vice... Mr. President...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為  執行總統簽署的命令\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I believe it is our duty to carry out the orders
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.59,0:29:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們的職責\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that the president signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.15,0:29:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-情況已經變了  -計劃依然可行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- The circumstances have changed. - The plan is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.33,0:29:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想怎么辦  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}So, what would you like to do, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.15,0:29:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續還是終止任務\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}continue the mission or abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.63,0:29:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再考慮考慮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Uh, I... I wanna think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.32,0:29:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按計劃他將在兩小時后降落\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's scheduled to land in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.75,0:29:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just want...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.37,0:30:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得考慮一下  我們休息一下吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've gotta think. Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.11,0:30:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得整理整理思緒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I, uh, I need to process all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.96,0:30:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.03,0:30:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統權衡過一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president weighed everything--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茜說得很有道理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Cathy brought up some good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.28,0:30:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她從最開始就反對這件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}She's been against this from the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.77,0:30:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總統明確\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but the president clearly--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.58,0:30:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我點時間  道格  求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Just give me some time, Doug, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.10,0:30:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我耳邊吼的人太多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've got too many people barking in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.77,0:30:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統已經做完手術\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The president is out of surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.23,0:30:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他病情穩定但依然危重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and he is in stable but critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.16,0:30:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  聽我說  我們要有序得來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Excuse me! Excuse me! We are going to keep this orderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.02,0:30:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先讓薩克遜醫生發表完聲明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Dr. Saxon will finish his statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.89,0:30:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我們再回答你們的問題  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and then we'll answer your questions. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.32,0:30:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術進行了6小時28分鐘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The surgery lasted six hours, 28 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.00,0:31:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切除了四分之三的肝臟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Three quarters of his liver was removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.33,0:31:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝臟  哪怕只剩四分之一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}A liver, even one quarter of a liver,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.54,0:31:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有能力在六至八周內再生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}has the ability to regenerate within six to eight weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們每小時都會對他進行血檢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We will be conducting blood tests every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.15,0:31:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,監測肝酶水平  血氨水平  凝血酶原時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Enzymes, ammonia levels, PT times,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.22,0:31:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些在聲明材料上都有說明\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I believe these are all explained in the handout.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.66,0:31:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...醫學報告  我們馬上就繼續\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}...the medical report, live from the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.59,0:31:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宮的現場直播\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}which we will return to shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.62,0:31:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們在密切關注一則重大新聞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}But we have breaking news we're following.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此前的報道稱  未遂刺客是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The would-be assassin was previously reported
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.25,0:31:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄亥俄州代頓的約翰·卡萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}as John Carlyle from Dayton, Ohio,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.24,0:31:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在司法部的消息源稱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but sources in the Department of Justice now say
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.59,0:31:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這其實是盧卡斯·古德溫的化名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}this was actually an alias for Lucas Goodwin,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.95,0:31:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾是《華盛頓先驅報》的編輯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}a former editor at The Washington Herald
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.68,0:31:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年前被判犯下了網絡恐怖主義罪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who was convicted of cyberterrorism nearly two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.89,0:31:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們暫停這段手機拍攝的槍擊視頻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Now, if we freeze this cell phone footage of the shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.53,0:31:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后將槍手的臉與古德溫的照片進行對比\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and we compare the shooter's face to this picture of Goodwin...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.82,0:31:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對比結果驚人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}well, the comparison is striking
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.35,0:31:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也證實了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and would seem to confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.59,0:31:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自司法部消息源的說法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}what we're hearing from our sources in the DOJ,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.79,0:31:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即古德溫已于近日獲釋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who say Goodwin was recently released
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.12,0:31:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并加入了證人保護計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and is in a witness protection program.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.86,0:32:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好怪  想到我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's so strange to think that I--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.41,0:32:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久  也就兩小時前吧  還不到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It was, what? Just two hours before? Less than.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.64,0:32:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是什么反應\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How did he react?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.47,0:32:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很冷漠吧  我看不透他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He was cold, I guess. I couldn't really read him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.27,0:32:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起來好虛弱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He looks so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.05,0:32:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我回華盛頓嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Should I come back to Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.15,0:32:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看接下來幾天的情況吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's see how the next couple of days go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.36,0:32:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時通知我  我立馬上飛機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, just say the word, I'm on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.41,0:32:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  謝謝  莉安  晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All right, thank you, LeAnn. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.85,0:32:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.52,0:32:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭西斯  能聽到嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Francis, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.93,0:32:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.23,0:32:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛跟艾迪的父母通了話  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I just spoke to Eddie's parents, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.62,0:32:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說您想給他們打電話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You said you wanted to call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.78,0:32:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.39,0:33:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德華不止是位英雄  密查姆太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Edward was more than a hero, Mrs. Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.69,0:33:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我們的朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He was our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.11,0:33:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常遺憾您失去了兒子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm so sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.91,0:33:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么我能為您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Please, let me know if there's anything
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.56,0:33:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和您的家人做的  務必告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can do for you and your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.36,0:33:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您隨時可以給我打電話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You can call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.62,0:33:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  太太  這是我的私人號碼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes, ma'am, that is my private number.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.91,0:33:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次深表遺憾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And again, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.44,0:33:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-盧卡斯·古德溫  -我們不知道他出獄了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Lucas Goodwin? - We didn't know he was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.97,0:33:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能  他被釋放了你卻不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How can that happen? He's released and you didn't know--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.21,0:33:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  說到威脅\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ma'am... as far as threats go,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.54,0:33:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最近幾乎都在忙著應付您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}we've been far more occupied with you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我們能合作  因為我需要您的幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm hoping that we can work together, because I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.78,0:33:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么幫  -副總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- How? - The vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.95,0:33:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們談過了  我告訴他我會陪他出面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We spoke. I told him I would appear with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.29,0:33:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是聲明的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Not the statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在有個決定難以定奪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's having trouble making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.26,0:34:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能跟我一起回白宮嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Can you come back to the White House with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.46,0:34:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事很嚴重  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's serious, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.17,0:34:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以在路上跟您說明情況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can fill you in on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.65,0:34:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿我的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll grab my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.42,0:34:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓你進去  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I can't let you go any farther, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.34,0:34:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的幕僚長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm his Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.04,0:34:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生 \N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.56,0:34:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只有醫生和第一夫人可以進去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Only doctors and the First Lady for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.83,0:34:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.15,0:34:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.88,0:35:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-累壞了  -肯定的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Exhausted. - I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.52,0:35:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定也累壞了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You must be, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.29,0:35:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有太多東西我不了解  快把我...搞暈了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's so much I don't know. It's... overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.50,0:35:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我已向第一夫人說明了米爾金行動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, I briefed the First Lady on the Milkin operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.76,0:35:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到她曾與俄羅斯有過直接交涉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I thought she might have some insight,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.88,0:35:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也許她會有一些見解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}given her experience working directly with Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.83,0:35:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道已經有很多人為你出謀劃策了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I know you've had a lot of people weigh in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重視你的建議  克萊爾  我很高興你能來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I value your input, Claire. I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-道格拉斯  能讓我們單獨談談嗎  -當然\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Douglas, will you give us a minute? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.45,0:35:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會跟內閣在一起  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be with the cabinet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.56,0:35:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道人們常說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}You know that thing that people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.68,0:35:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝不會讓你無法承受\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"God never gives you more than you can handle"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.46,0:35:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.68,0:35:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的瑪喬莉  愿主保佑她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}My Marjory, God bless her,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.83,0:35:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說那是屁話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}she said that was pure bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.94,0:35:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫正在與死神搏斗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, listen to me complaining
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.08,0:35:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻還得聽我抱怨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}while your husband is fighting for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.65,0:35:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關系  其實我需要分散下注意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Oh, it's okay. Actually, I need the distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.43,0:35:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們談談俄羅斯吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's talk Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.37,0:36:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很糾結  我們有架飛機在北海上空盤旋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm torn. Uh, we have this plane circling over the North Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.03,0:36:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不知道該怎么做  -你的直覺是什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- and I don't know what to do. - Well, what does your gut tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.77,0:36:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來就不是靠直覺做事的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I've never been a gut sort of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.85,0:36:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有把槍指在我頭上...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I mean, if I had a gun to my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.14,0:36:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-對不起  我比喻不當  -沒關系  繼續\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Sorry, that was a poor choice of words. - It's fine. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.90,0:36:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解總統希望達到的目的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I understand what the president hoped to achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.69,0:36:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一想到激怒俄羅斯...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}but the thought of provoking Russia...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.72,0:36:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這才剛開始了解此事的復雜性\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And I'm just beginning to immerse myself in all the complexities.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果換了弗蘭克  他會怎么做呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What would Frank do, if he were in my shoes right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.09,0:36:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他在這兒  他會告訴你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}If he were here, he'd tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.52,0:36:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你最不應該考慮的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}that's the last thing you should think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.51,0:36:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他不在這兒  你在\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}because he's not here, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.12,0:36:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會怎么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.07,0:36:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續這項任務還是叫他回來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Proceed with the mission or bring him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.15,0:36:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩者我都不喜歡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I don't like either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.62,0:36:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有這兩個選擇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Those are my options.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.11,0:36:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說在弗蘭西斯身邊28年  我學到了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Well, if there's one thing I've learned, 28 years with Francis,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.49,0:36:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是他重復多次的那句話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}and he said it time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.64,0:36:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如果你不喜歡餐具的擺放..."\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}"If you don't like the way the table is set..."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.99,0:37:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-"那就掀桌子"  -沒錯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- "Then turn over the table." - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟我說過不止一次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}He's said it to me, more than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.78,0:37:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就該這么做  唐納德\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Then that's what you should do, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.60,0:37:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但要怎么做呢  -我們一起想想吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- But how? - Well, let's figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.26,0:37:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是早該降落了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Weren't we supposed to have landed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.94,0:37:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在待命航線上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're in a holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.83,0:37:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么  出什么事了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Why? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.34,0:37:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我們在待命航線上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}All I know is we're in a holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.38,0:37:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道格\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.38,0:38:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這架飛機很快就會沒油\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This plane's gonna run out of fuel soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.27,0:38:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定要找個地方讓它降落\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We're gonna have to put it down somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.71,0:38:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就發表聲明  先跟記者團打聲招呼吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'll be making a statement shortly. Let's notify the press corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.78,0:38:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-關于行動嗎  -不  讓美國人民放心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- About the operation? - No, to reassure the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.94,0:38:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我在那邊等你嗎  -給我十分鐘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Shall I meet you in there? - Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.72,0:38:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內閣呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}The cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.85,0:38:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還在等您的決定  先生  -很好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Still waiting on your decision, sir. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.07,0:38:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.76,0:38:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把飛機降落在中國\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I want you to land the plane in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.59,0:38:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中國嗎  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}China, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.73,0:38:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有中國的錢就沒有救市計劃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}There's no bailout without Chinese money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.04,0:38:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把米爾金給他們  他們會有更多籌碼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}We give them Milkin, they have more leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  那我們就沒有籌碼了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, that gives away our leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.77,0:38:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不贊成政權更迭  但那是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}I'm not for regime change, but that just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.39,0:38:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是佩特羅夫最想不到的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's the last thing that Petrov is expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.18,0:39:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會索要東西伯利亞的鉆井權\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}They'll demand drilling access in eastern Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.70,0:39:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他們提出  我們就是兩害中較輕的那個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And when they do, we become the lesser of two evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.43,0:39:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  總統從未打算\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Sir, at no time did the president
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.26,0:39:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把中國攪進來...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}intend on bringing China into the mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.00,0:39:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓飛機降落在中國領土上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Get the plane on Chinese soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.80,0:39:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且移交米爾金的資產  這就是我的決定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}And turn over Milkin's assets. That's my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我是向你求助的  -我也給予了幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- I asked for your help. - And that's what I gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.36,0:39:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  中國不在總統的計劃范圍內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}No, China wasn't part of the president's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.31,0:39:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在代總統的計劃范圍內\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}It's part of the acting president's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.66,0:39:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你準備好了嗎  -好了  就等你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- You ready? - Yes, whenever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.57,0:39:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-賽斯  -是  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}- Seth? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.85,0:39:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士們先生們  有請代總統\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Ladies and gentlemen, the acting president.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.55,0:39:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天對所有美國民眾來說都是艱難的一天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}This is a difficult day for all Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.91,0:39:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是對安德伍德夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}particularly for Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.21,0:39:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感謝她能來到這兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}who is gracious enough to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.14,0:40:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我向焦慮的國民講話時  給我力量\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}to lend me strength while I address an anxious nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.97,0:40:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑}Mr. President!
